<title>USA: Duff reaffirms ServiceMaster single-A-minus rating.</title>
<headline>Duff reaffirms ServiceMaster single-A-minus rating.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1996-12-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Duff &amp; Phelps Credit Rating Co said it has reaffirmed its single-A-minus rating on senior notes of ServiceMaster LP after ServiceMaster's announcement on Thursday of a definitive agreement to buy Barefoot Inc.</p>
<p>Duff, in a statement dated December 5, said the action covers about $501 million of ServiceMaster's debt.</p>
<p>In the acquisition, ServiceMaster will offer Barefoot stockholders $16 per share either in cash or an equivalent amount of ServiceMaster shares. The transaction's aggregate value is about $230 million.</p>
<p>((--Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
